[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    398[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m2[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mRead commands have non-trivial cost in the EHR audit.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The EHR's audit is the institution's record of who accessed whose chart. Duplicate access events inflate the audit log volume, complicate forensic reconstruction, and (in some EHR vendors' audit reports) can trigger anomaly-detection alerts as the duplicate access pattern looks like a clinician browsing the patient's chart repeatedly.[K
