[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    645[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m2[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mWebSocket connection limits.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m API Gateway's account-level concurrent-connection limits and per-source-IP rate-limits bound the maximum simultaneous voice sessions. For a large health system with thousands of clinicians, the limits matter. The architecture should specify reserved-capacity-or-quota-increase as a deployment-time activity.[K
