[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    651[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Add a "WebSocket Audio Streaming" prose paragraph in the AWS Implementation section that specifies the connection-time authentication mechanism (Lambda authorizer with the clinician's Cognito token), the connection-limit and rate-limit considerations (with quota increase as a deployment-time activity), the idle-timeout interaction with session-state staleness, and the binary-message-type frame format.[K
